{"ref":"R4649410","lang":"1,2","upstream_status":200,"upstream_url":"https://webapi.resales-online.com/V6/PropertyDetails?p1=1004678&p2=<redacted>&P_RefId=R4649410&p_Lang=1%2C2&p_agency_filterid=1","upstream_content_type":"application/json","via_fixie":true,"elapsed_ms":114,"body":{"transaction":{"status":"success","incomingIp":"54.217.142.99","version":"6","subversion":"6.0","service":"Property Details","datetime":"05-05-2026 12:01:06"},"QueryInfo":{"ApiId":"74269","QueryId":""},"Property":{"Reference":"R4649410","AgencyRef":"","Status":{"system":"Available","en":"Available","es":"Disponible"},"Country":"Spain","Province":"Málaga","Area":"Costa del Sol","Location":"Guadalmina Baja","SubLocation":"","PropertyType":{"en":{"NameType":"Detached Villa","Type":"House","TypeId":"2-1","Subtype1":"Detached Villa","SubtypeId1":"2-2"},"es":{"NameType":"Villa - Chalet","Type":"Casa","TypeId":"2-1","Subtype1":"Villa - Chalet","SubtypeId1":"2-2"}},"Bedrooms":"4","Bathrooms":"5","Currency":"EUR","Price":4199999,"OriginalPrice":4200000,"Community_Fees_Year":"2,820","Basura_Tax_Year":"0","IBI_Fees_Year":"6,188","Dimensions":"Metres","Built":555,"Terrace":64,"GardenPlot":2500,"EnergyRating":{"CO2Rated":"","CO2Value":"","EnergyRated":"","EnergyValue":"","Image":""},"OwnProperty":"0","Pool":1,"Parking":1,"Garden":1,"CompletionDate":"1972-01-01","BuiltYear":"1972","Description":{"en":"UNIQUE LOCATION- EXCELLENT INVESTMENT\r\n\r\nExtraordinary villa with a unique location on the golf course in Guadalmina Baja, just 200 meters from the sea! This fantastic property boasts four bedrooms, each with its own en-suite bathroom. The master bedroom stands out with its spacious layout, featuring a cozy fireplace, walk-in closet, and a sizable terrace overlooking the meticulously maintained garden. Enjoy breathtaking views of the golf course and garden from the large windows and French balconies in every bedroom.\r\n\r\nThe heart of the villa is the living room, characterized by its impressive ceiling height and welcoming fireplace. Natural light floods the space through the expansive windows, offering direct access to the garden. A library located above the living room provides a serene space for reading and relaxation. The dining room is perfect for hosting large gatherings, with direct access to the patio. The well-equipped kitchen boasts ample cooking space, accompanied by a dining area ideal for breakfast.\r\n\r\nIndulge in the spa facilities, complete with the option to install a jacuzzi, sauna, and access to the roof terrace. The lower level features a heated saltwater pool with an electric cover, a garden cinema, and a charming lounge area resembling a &quot;tree house.&quot;\r\n\r\nThe garden is a sanctuary of fruit trees, including peach, apricot, fig, orange, grapefruit, lunario lemons, lime, Australian lemon, kumquat, mandarin, and papaya, complemented by an extensive collection of over 15 different rose varieties.\r\n\r\nConvenient amenities include a garage for two cars, a driveway with space for eight cars, multiple storage rooms, a boiler room, technical room with an alarm system, and a separate room for pool equipment. The property is heated by solar panels, heat pumps, and gas.\r\n\r\nDon&apos;t miss this outstanding opportunity to own a truly remarkable villa in Guadalmina Baja, perfectly situated on the golf course.\r\n\r\nEasy viewings- Contact for viewing!\r\n\r\n\r\n","es":"UBICACIÓN ÚNICA- EXCELENTE INVERSIÓN\r\n\r\nExtraordinaria villa con una ubicación única en el campo de golf de Guadalmina Baja, ¡a sólo 200 metros del mar! Esta fantástica propiedad cuenta con cuatro dormitorios, cada uno con su propio baño en suite. El dormitorio principal destaca por su amplia distribución, con una acogedora chimenea, vestidor y una amplia terraza con vistas al jardín meticulosamente cuidado. Disfrute de impresionantes vistas del campo de golf y el jardín desde los grandes ventanales y balcones franceses de cada habitación.\r\n\r\nEl corazón de la villa es el salón, caracterizado por su impresionante altura de techo y su acogedora chimenea. La luz natural inunda el espacio a través de los amplios ventanales, ofreciendo acceso directo al jardín. Una biblioteca ubicada encima de la sala de estar ofrece un espacio sereno para la lectura y la relajación. El comedor es perfecto para celebrar grandes reuniones, con acceso directo al patio. La cocina bien equipada cuenta con un amplio espacio para cocinar, acompañada de un comedor ideal para el desayuno.\r\n\r\nDisfrute de las instalaciones del spa, que cuentan con la opción de instalar un jacuzzi, sauna y acceso a la terraza de la azotea. El nivel inferior cuenta con una piscina climatizada de agua salada con cubierta eléctrica, un cine en el jardín y una encantadora sala de estar que se asemeja a una &quot;casa en el árbol&quot;.\r\n\r\nEl jardín es un santuario de árboles frutales, como duraznos, albaricoques, higueras, naranjas, pomelos, limones lunario, limas, limones australianos, kumquat, mandarinas y papayas, complementados con una extensa colección de más de 15 variedades diferentes de rosas.\r\n\r\nLas comodidades convenientes incluyen un garaje para dos autos, un camino de entrada con espacio para ocho autos, múltiples trasteros, una sala de calderas, una sala técnica con sistema de alarma y una sala separada para equipos de piscina. La propiedad se calienta mediante paneles solares, bombas de calor y gas.\r\n\r\nNo pierda esta excelente oportunidad de poseer una villa verdaderamente extraordinaria en Guadalmina Baja, perfectamente situada en el campo de golf.\r\n\r\nVisitas fáciles: ¡póngase en contacto para verlas!"},"PropertyFeatures":{"en":{"Category":[{"Type":"Setting","Value":["Frontline Golf","Suburban","Beachside","Close To Golf","Close To Shops","Close To Sea","Close To Town","Close To Schools"]},{"Type":"Orientation","Value":["North","North East","East","South East","South","South West","West","North West"]},{"Type":"Condition","Value":["Excel